Citation.sTitle: Measurement and Correlation of Griseofulvin Solubility in Different Solvents at Temperatures from (281.95 to 357.60) K
Citation.sAbstract: The solubility of griseofulvin in acetone, 2-butanone, 1,2-dichloroethane, N,N-dimethylacetamide, dimethyl sulfoxide, and N-methyl-2-pyrrolidone have been determined by the dynamic method. The experimental data were well-correlated with the modified Apelblat equation.
